# --- .NET build artifacts ---
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/publish/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# --- Visual Studio / Rider / VS Code ---
.vs/
.idea/
.vscode/
*.lock.json

# --- Runtime / per-user data (next to .exe) ---
**/settings.json
**/stats.json
**/achievements.json
**/current_game.json
**/last_game.log
**/crash.log

# --- Distribution archives (rebuilt by `dotnet publish`) ---
*.zip

# --- Generated release output (built by `dotnet publish` then assembled by hand) ---
release/publish/
release/*.zip
release/Parcheesi-Access-v*/

# --- Audio diagnostic log (only created if a sound asset fails to load) ---
**/audio_load.log

# --- OS junk ---
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
desktop.ini

# --- Tooling-specific (do not commit) ---
.claude/
